<p class="mt-50 font-weight-bold">
    DA PARTICIPAÇÃO DO EXECUTIVO (PLAYER) |
    <span class="text-primary font-italic">
        OF THE EXECUTIVE’S (PLAYER’S) ATTENDANCE
    </span>
</p>
<ol class="text-justify">
    <li class="mt-20">
        Os Players deverão preencher a ficha de inscrição da empresa e de seus representantes até o dia <span class="font-weight-bold">29 de dezembro de 2021</span> na plataforma online <span class="font-weight-bold">MyRio2C</span> do <span class="font-weight-bold">Rio2C</span>, através do link enviado por e-mail pela organização do evento. Essa inscrição irá gerar o perfil do Player no sistema e o acesso será personalizado através de senha. |
        <span class="text-primary font-italic">
            The Player is requested to fill out the company and its representative’s registration form by <span class="font-weight-bold">December 29<sup>th</sup>, 2021</span> on <span class="font-weight-bold">Rio2C’s</span> online platform <span class="font-weight-bold">MyRio2C</span> using the link forwarded via e-mail by the event organizers. This registration generates the Player’s profile on the system, which shall be personalized by using a password.
        </span>
    </li>
    <li class="mt-20">
        A partir do dia <span class="font-weight-bold">10 de fevereiro até 07 de março de 2022</span> todos os executivos que representarão o Player terão acesso aos projetos inscritos em uma área exclusiva na plataforma online <span class="font-weight-bold">MyRio2C</span> do <span class="font-weight-bold">Rio2C</span>. Para avaliar seus projetos, o executivo deverá acessar a plataforma do evento com seu login e senha. |
        <span class="text-primary font-italic">
            Starting from February <span class="font-weight-bold">10<sup>th</sup> until March 7<sup>th</sup>, 2022</span>, all executives (Players) will have access to the submitted projects in <span class="font-weight-bold">MyRio2C</span> a dedicated area of <span class="font-weight-bold">Rio2C’s</span> online platform. To evaluate your projects, the executive must access the event’s platform with their login and password.
        </span>
    </li>
    <li class="mt-20">
        Os Players terão até o dia <span class="font-weight-bold">07 de março de 2022</span> para selecionar os projetos cujos Participantes desejam se reunir. |
        <span class="text-primary font-italic">
            Players shall have until <span class="font-weight-bold">March 07<sup>th</sup>, 2022</span> to mark which projects’ proposing Participants they would like to meet up with.
        </span>
    </li>
</ol>
